The project focused on requirements of study success and collected a variety of data on the student cohort in winter 2014 and summer 2015. This includes  quantitative and qualitative data from interviews as well as non-responsive  data from exams and the administrative departments. A major data analyis and interpretation as well as a thorough description of the research project and  its data is scheduled for publication as a PhD paper in 2020 at the University of Stuttgart. The dataset also includes the surveys and a codebook.
